trans-unit.source: Describes the referential constraints on the relationships in a conceptual model.
trans-unit.target: 描述对概念模型中的关系的引用约束。

trans-unit.source: Gets the built-in type kind for this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" />.
trans-unit.target: 获取此 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> 的内置类型种类。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.BuiltInTypeKind" /> object that represents the built-in type kind for this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" />.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.BuiltInTypeKind" /> 对象，表示此 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> 的内置类型种类。

trans-unit.source: Gets the list of properties for the "from role" on which this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> is defined.
trans-unit.target: 获取定义此 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> 时使用的“源角色”的属性列表。

trans-unit.source: A collection of type <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection`1" /> that contains the list of properties for "from role" on which this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> is defined.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection`1" /> 类型的集合，其中包含定义此 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> 时使用的“源角色”的属性列表。

trans-unit.source: Gets the "from role" that takes part in this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" />.
trans-unit.target: 获取参与此 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> 的“源角色”。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.RelationshipEndMember" /> object that represents the "from role" that takes part in this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" />.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.RelationshipEndMember" /> 对象，表示参与此 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> 的“源角色”。

trans-unit.source: Gets the list of properties for the "to role" on which this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> is defined.
trans-unit.target: 获取定义此 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> 时使用的“目标角色”的属性列表。

trans-unit.source: A collection of type <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection`1" /> that contains the list of properties for the "to role" on which this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> is defined.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection`1" /> 类型的集合，其中包含定义此 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> 时使用的“目标角色”的属性列表。

trans-unit.source: Gets the "to role" that takes part in this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" />.
trans-unit.target: 获取参与此 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> 的“目标角色”。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.RelationshipEndMember" /> object that represents the "to role" that takes part in this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" />.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.RelationshipEndMember" /> 对象，表示参与此 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> 的“目标角色”。

trans-unit.source: Returns the combination of the names of the <see cref="P:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint.FromRole" /> and the <see cref="P:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint.ToRole" />.
trans-unit.target: 返回 <see cref="P:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint.FromRole" /> 和 <see cref="P:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint.ToRole" /> 的名称组合。

trans-unit.source: The combination of the names of the <see cref="P:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint.FromRole" /> and the <see cref="P:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint.ToRole" />.
